35namespace cricket {
36
37struct MediaEngineDependencies {
38 MediaEngineDependencies() = default;
39 MediaEngineDependencies(const MediaEngineDependencies&) = delete;
40 MediaEngineDependencies(MediaEngineDependencies&&) = default;
41 MediaEngineDependencies& operator=(const MediaEngineDependencies&) = delete;
42 MediaEngineDependencies& operator=(MediaEngineDependencies&&) = default;
43 ~MediaEngineDependencies() = default;
44
45 webrtc::TaskQueueFactory* task_queue_factory = nullptr;
46 rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioDeviceModule> adm;
47 rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioEncoderFactory> audio_encoder_factory;
48 rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioDecoderFactory> audio_decoder_factory;
49 rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioMixer> audio_mixer;
50 rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioProcessing> audio_processing;
51 webrtc::AudioFrameProcessor* audio_frame_processor = nullptr;
52
53 std::unique_ptr<webrtc::VideoEncoderFactory> video_encoder_factory;
54 std::unique_ptr<webrtc::VideoDecoderFactory> video_decoder_factory;
55
56 const webrtc::WebRtcKeyValueConfig* trials = nullptr;
57};
58
59// CreateMediaEngine may be called on any thread, though the engine is
60// only expected to be used on one thread, internally called the "worker
61// thread". This is the thread Init must be called on.
62RTC_EXPORT std::unique_ptr<MediaEngineInterface> CreateMediaEngine(
63 MediaEngineDependencies dependencies);
64
65// Verify that extension IDs are within 1-byte extension range and are not
66// overlapping.
67bool ValidateRtpExtensions(const std::vector<webrtc::RtpExtension>& extensions);
68
69// Discard any extensions not validated by the 'supported' predicate. Duplicate
70// extensions are removed if 'filter_redundant_extensions' is set, and also any
71// mutually exclusive extensions (see implementation for details) are removed.
72std::vector<webrtc::RtpExtension> FilterRtpExtensions(
73 const std::vector<webrtc::RtpExtension>& extensions,
74 bool (*supported)(absl::string_view),
75 bool filter_redundant_extensions,
76 const webrtc::WebRtcKeyValueConfig& trials);
77
78webrtc::BitrateConstraints GetBitrateConfigForCodec(const Codec& codec);
79
80} // namespace cricket
